<div class="content-img-wrapper ">
<div class="image-pinit-wrapper">
<img src="http://f.tqn.com/y/goperu/1/S/3/D/-/-/peru_haunted_hotel_bolivar_lima.jpg" alt="Gran Hotel Bolivar - Francisco Anzola, flickr.com" class="" data-description="The Most Haunted Places in Peru: Ghosts of the Gran Hotel Bol&amp;iacute;var, Lima" itemprop="image" >
<a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://goperu.about.com/od/sightsandattractions/ss/The-Most-Haunted-Places-in-Peru.htm?utm_source=pinterest&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=shareurlbuttons_nip&media=http://f.tqn.com/y/goperu/1/S/3/D/-/-/peru_haunted_hotel_bolivar_lima.jpg&description=The Most Haunted Places in Peru: Ghosts of the Gran Hotel Bol&amp;iacute;var, Lima" data-component="stepbystepImage" data-source="pinitBtn" data-type="sharePinterest" data-ordinal="2" data-network="pinterest" title="Pin to Pinterest" class="pinit-btn" data-pin-do="skipLink"></a> </div>
